{"tid":702562,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣東道IT男墮樓 跌入貨車車斗","createTime":"2018-06-15T04:12:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-15T04:14:46.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3cc891ad20dbd9cbec879e49e52033209e4f7ccb","tid":702562,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T04:12:49.000Z","msg":"旺角廣東道1156號對開，昨晨7時許，一名中年男子從高處墮下，跌在停泊路邊的一輛貨車車斗內，重傷昏迷。救護員到場將他送院搶救，目前情況危殆。傷者姓杜49歲，警方列企圖自殺案處理。據稱，事主做IT，獨居上述大廈的4樓單位。<br />\n<br />\n該貨車屬於現場一間建築材料公司，女東主稱，早上她在茶餐廳吃早餐，有街坊走來告知有人跌在貨車車斗內，她連忙趕回查看並報警，她估計事主已經墮下兩三小時「應該5點左右發生」。其後更得知事主竟然是她相熟的舊街坊。女東主哽咽說：「由細玩到大，好熟，佢父母移民咗去加拿大。好愕然，之前都唔覺佢有咩唔妥。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180615/20421621\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180615%2F20421621&d=pJmRmfFXVjkpliUNsRgPqzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=2cab9e96\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180615%2F20421621&h=5d59e232\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180615/20421621</a>"},{"pid":"fe52a8a55f275bb7a1cba670c4a1152889bfaff4","tid":702562,"uid":113626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T04:14:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 首抽中香港仲要加埋IT"}]}